stand-alone basis or in collaboration with local business partners), including operating in accordance with the U.S. Foreign
Corrupt Practices Act (the “FCPA”) and applicable local laws and customs;
•unfavorable tax treatment or adverse changes to tax policy;
•adverse weather conditions;
