start-up expense at our second facility in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam in early 2019. During 2018, we incurred production start-up
expense for the transition to Series 6 module manufacturing at our facilities in Kulim, Malaysia and Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.
We also incurred production start-up expense for the transition to Series 6 module manufacturing at our facility in Perrysburg, Ohio
in early 2018.
