of substrate glass and $500 million of cover glass.
(3) In connection  with business or project acquisitions, we may agree to pay additional amounts to the selling parties upon achievement of
certain milestones. See Note 14. “Commitments and Contingencies”  to our consolidated financial statements for further information.
